# NO COUNTRIES ON ONLYFANSSEARCH

## The Rule

**Countries DO NOT EXIST as a separate concept on Erogram.**

When a country (e.g. France, Germany) is added to OnlyFans Search, it is added as a **CATEGORY** — exactly the same as "Brunette", "Asian", "Latina", etc.

- NEVER create `OF_COUNTRIES`, `OF_COUNTRY_SLUGS`, `OF_COUNTRY_MAP`, or any country-specific data structures
- NEVER create `/country/` routes or country URL helpers (`ofCountryUrl`, `ofCountryCategoryUrl`)
- NEVER add country vs. category branching logic — there is only ONE type: category
- If the owner wants to add "France", add it to `OF_CATEGORIES` in `constants.ts`
- Country pages like `/onlyfansfrance` do not exist. Use `/{slug}onlyfans` like every other category

## Why

Countries were removed because 19 out of 20 had 0 creators. The entire country infrastructure was dead code generating empty pages that hurt SEO. The owner decided countries = categories, period.
